title: FIGHT FOR IT

description:
FIGHT FOR IT! There are going to be times when people tell you what you can or can't do but just remember, who you are fighting for! Best Motivational Speech featuring Ronald A. Burgess Jr. (https://bit.ly/RonaldABurgessJrMotiversity).


Music by Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube), Rok Nardin (https://bit.ly/RokNardinMusic), and Whitesand (https://www.youtube.com/c/WhitesandComposer).
